'''Ethics''' (from the [[Ancient Greek]] {{polytonic|ἠθικός}} ''ēthikos'', the adjective of {{polytonic|ἤθος}} ''ēthos'' "custom, habit"), a major branch of [[philosophy]],including genetics is the study of [[Value theory|value]]s and [[Custom (law)|custom]]s of a person or group.
